<h3 id=3D"APIDesignStandards-GET">GET</h3>
<p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">GET is to be used for safe to rep=
eat queries. The use of GET must not lead to a change of resource state, bu=
t it is valid for resource state to change between queries due to other imp=
acting factors.</span></p>
<p><span style=3D"letter-spacing: 0.0px;">The use of GET shall not require =
any data payload for normal query operations. Use of query parameters is th=
e correct way to search for data. If there is a concern that PII may be in =
the URI and it is desirable to avoid this due to server log caching concern=
s then either:</span></p>
<ul>
<li>PREFERRED: Abstract the PII into the user=E2=80=99s identity and establ=
ish the data as part of the authentication process.</li>
<li>BACKUP OPTION: Use a POST to create a query request resource and return=
 a response ID, then use GET against that ID to obtain the results.&nbsp;<e=
m>Note this is also a pattern for queries which may take time to complete.<=
/em></li>
<li>NOT PREFERRED: Use a POST with query data in the body and return a resp=
onse set to this call.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Examples:</strong></p>
<p>GET /customers/12345</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom" style=3D"borde=
r-bottom-width: 1px;">
<b class=3D"code-title">GET request: single resource</b><span class=3D"coll=
apse-source expand-control" style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-c=
ontrol-icon icon">&nbsp;</span><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand s=
ource</span></span><span class=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: false; theme: Confluence; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Confl=
uence">GET /customers/12345 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json</pre>
</div>
</div>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom" style=3D"borde=
r-bottom-width: 1px;">
<b class=3D"code-title">GET response: single resource</b><span class=3D"col=
lapse-source expand-control" style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expand-=
control-icon icon">&nbsp;</span><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expand =
source</span></span><span class=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: false; theme: Confluence; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Confl=
uence">HTTP/1.1 200 Ok
Content-Type: application/json
=20
{
    "data": {
        "customerId": {
            "id" : "12345",
            "idScheme": "CustomerInternalId"
        },
        "firstName": "Samuel",
        "lastName": "Johnson",
        "middleName": "Andrew",
        "dateOfBirth": "1998-07-03",
        "gender": {
            "code": "M"
        },
        "status": {
            "code": "A"
        }
    }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p><br></p>
<p>GET /customers</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl hide-border-bottom" style=3D"borde=
r-bottom-width: 1px;">
<b class=3D"code-title">GET request: collection resource</b><span class=3D"=
collapse-source expand-control" style=3D"display:none;"><span class=3D"expa=
nd-control-icon icon">&nbsp;</span><span class=3D"expand-control-text">Expa=
nd source</span></span><span class=3D"collapse-spinner-wrapper"></span>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl hide-toolbar">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: js; gutter: false; theme: Confluence; collapse: true" data-theme=3D"Confl=
uence">GET /customers HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json</pre>
</div>
</div>
