</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Rename o=
r delete an existing operation</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1"><p>No</p=
></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Change c=
ardinality of a field from 1 to n or n to 1</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">No</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Add new =
http status code</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">No</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Add new =
error code</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Yes</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Enhance =
enum(s) to add more values in request</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Yes</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Enhance =
enum(s) to add more values in response</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">No</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Change m=
andatory request field(query,request body,header) to optional</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Yes</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Change d=
ata types in request /response</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">No</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Change /=
 Remove enum values in request / response</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">No</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Change/ =
remove existing endpoint names</td>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">No</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"tf-rowspan-1 tf-colspan-1 confluenceTd" colspan=3D"1">Change /=
 remove existing http status codes / error codes</td>
